limited edition memorabilia

19
00:02:33,541 --> 00:02:35,500
that you can't
find anywhere!

20
00:02:35,583 --> 00:02:37,208
Then you put 'em up
in your own room!

21
00:02:37,291 --> 00:02:38,666
