handle a comeback?

64
00:04:45,333 --> 00:04:48,041
She says she's going
to sing no matter what.

65
00:04:48,125 --> 00:04:49,458
Well, this isn't Tokyo.

66
00:04:49,541 --> 00:04:52,208
