immortal corpses.

77
00:05:13,583 --> 00:05:14,750
Shikabane Hime?

78
00:05:14,833 --> 00:05:16,375
What the hell is
a Shikabane Hime?

79
00:05:16,458 --> 00:05:18,458
Tell me who you are,
you son of a--

80
00:05:23,541 --> 00:05:30,375
[Disconnect tone]

81
00:05:34,416 --> 00:05:35,916
Is this all
you could find?

82
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,416
